                                        "},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"text","text":"From each of the 10 factors we have to take one power: or x^0, or x^1, or x^2. Choose 3 times x^2, 1 times x^1 and 6 times x^0. This can be done in "},{"type":"katex","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\frac{10!}{3! x 1! x 6!}"}],"attrs":{"inline":true}},{"type":"text","text":" = 840 ways. Or choose 2 times x^2, 3 times x^1 and 5 times x^0 in "},{"type":"katex","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\frac{10!}{2! x 3! x 5!}"}],"attrs":{"inline":true}},{"type":"text","text":" = 2520 ways. Or choose 1 times x^2, 5 times x^5 and 4 times x^0 in "},{"type":"katex","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\frac{10!}{1! x 5! x 4!}"}],"attrs":{"inline":true}},{"type":"text","text":" = 1260 ways. Or choose 7 times x^1 and 3 times x^0 in "},{"type":"katex","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\frac{10!}{7! x 3!}"}],"attrs":{"inline":true}},{"type":"text","text":" = 120 ways. The coefficient of x^7 is 840 + 2520 + 1260 + 120 = 4740."}]},{"type":"text","text":"



                            "}]}

