"},{"type":"paragraph","content":[{"type":"katex","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\begin{aligned} \int_4^{1000000} \frac 1{\sqrt[3] x} dx < & \sum_{k=a}^b \frac 1{\sqrt[3] n} < \int_3^{1000001} \frac 1{\sqrt[3] x} dx & \small \color{#3D99F6} \text{Note that }\frac 1{ \sqrt[3]x} \text{ is a convex function.} 
\\ \frac {3x^\frac 23}2\bigg|_4^{1000000} < & \sum_{k=a}^b \frac 1{\sqrt[3] n} < \frac {3x^\frac 23}2\bigg|_3^{1000001}
